description: Morana`s Mamoswine battled against Chili`s Pansear in a match that would close the Striaton Gym if Chili lost. The type advantage that Chili`s Pansear over Morana`s Mamoswine proved ineffective as Morana`s Mamoswine countered that disadvantage with power. Morana`s Mamoswine won the match.
name: Manmoo (Drago)
